item.title: 36C3 Querying
item.description: 0x0. Introduction This Challenge was part of the 36C3 Junior CTF. It was a “Web” challenge with a difficulty rating of “Medium”, you were given an URL for the live challenge server and also a copy of the server (with a fake flag obv) as a Docker Container to run locally to test your exploits.
